imageDescription: In the image, there is a heart-shaped bank vault with a shattered lock, symbolizing a heart that has been broken and robbed. The bank vault is floating in the sky, surrounded by clouds, representing the emotional high and escape the song describes. The heart-shaped vault is also overflowing with money and love notes, illustrating the intense and all-consuming nature of the relationship.
